'''愛黛兒·勞麗·布鲁·阿德金斯'''<ref name=nicole/>，{{Post-nominals|MBE|country=GBR}}（{{Lang-en|Adele Laurie Blue Adkins}}，<small>英語發音：</small>{{IPAc-en|ə|ˈ|d|ɛ|l}}，{{bd|1988年|5月5日|catIdx=Adele}}），是一名英國知名創作歌手。2006年，愛黛兒從{{Le|BRIT學校|BRIT School}}的“表演藝術與技術專業”畢業後，她的朋友把她的樣曲上傳到[[Myspace|Myspace]]，由此愛黛兒獲得了[[XL唱片|XL唱片]]的合約。2007年，她獲得了[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]的“樂評人選擇獎”，並赢得了[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]2008年[[年度新聲|年度新聲]]的評選。她的首張專輯《[[19_(專輯)|19]]》於2008年發行，該專輯在英國獲得了8×[[音樂唱片銷售認證列表|白金]]的認證，在美國獲得3×白金的認證<ref name="BPI certifications">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certifiedawards/search.aspx|title=Certified Awards Search|publisher=[[英國唱片業協會|British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=2011-03-01|archive-date=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5mr0Evm3j?url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certifiedawards/search.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=SEARCH_RESULTS |title=Recording Industry Association of America |publisher=RIAA |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2008-09-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5aWxoHiRP?url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=SEARCH_RESULTS |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在商業和評價上都獲得了成功，專輯中包含了她16歲時以家鄉倫敦西諾伍德的郊區為背景寫的第一首歌《{{Le|榮耀故鄉|Hometown Glory}}》。2008年末，愛黛兒參與了《[[周六夜現場|周六夜現場]]》的錄製，進一步推動她的事業於美國發展。在2009年的[[第51屆葛萊美獎|第51屆葛萊美獎]]上，她奪得了“[[葛萊美獎最佳新人|最佳新人]]”及“{{Le|葛萊美獎最佳流行女歌手|Grammy Award for Best Female Pop Vocal Performance|最佳流行女歌手}}”獎項<ref name=GRAM09>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1139346/Brits-Duffy-Adele-Coldplay-clinch-awards-lead-British-winners-Grammys.html|title=Brits on top: Duffy, Adele and Coldplay clinch top awards as they lead British winners at Grammys|work=Daily Mail|location=London|publisher={{tsl|en|Associated Newspapers||Associated Newspapers}}|date=2011-02-09|accessdate=2011-07-12|archive-date=2013-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115042902/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1139346/Brits-Duffy-Adele-Coldplay-clinch-awards-lead-British-winners-Grammys.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Jody Thompson |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/news/2009/02/09/coldplay-led-zepellin-s-robert-plant-radiohead-duffy-and-adele-win-at-grammy-awards-after-rihanna-pulls-out-of-show-115875-21109334/ |title=Coldplay, Robert Plant, Radiohead, Duffy and Adele win at Grammy Awards after Rihanna pulls out of show – 3am & Mirror Online |publisher=Mirror.co.uk |date=2009-02-09 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2011-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208224406/http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/news/2009/02/09/coldplay-led-zepellin-s-robert-plant-radiohead-duffy-and-adele-win-at-grammy-awards-after-rihanna-pulls-out-of-show-115875-21109334/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年初，愛黛兒發行了她的第二張錄音室專輯《[[21_(愛黛兒專輯）|21]]》，這張專輯獲得了廣泛好評，並超越了她首張專輯的成功<ref name="110208Charts">{{Cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/02/british-soul-singer-adele-preps-summer-us-tour.html|title=British soul singer Adele preps summer U.S. tour|date=2011-02-08|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2011-05-08|archive-date=2011-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211105216/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/02/british-soul-singer-adele-preps-summer-us-tour.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這張專輯在2012年赢得了{{Le|愛黛兒獲得的獎項和提名名單|List of awards and nominations received by Adele|大量歌唱類獎項}}，{{Le|葛萊美獎紀錄|Grammy Award records|破紀錄}}地獲得了包括“{{Le|格莱美奖年度专辑|Grammy Award for Album of the Year|年度专辑}}”在内的六項[[葛萊美獎|格莱美奖]]、包括“全英年度專輯”在内的兩項[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]以及三項[[全美音樂獎|全美音乐奖]]，該專輯在英國獲得了17×[[音樂唱片銷售認證列表|白金]]的認證，成为了英国史上[[英国最畅销专辑列表|第四名最畅销的专辑]]；在美國，专辑被认证为14×白金（[[RIAA认证|钻石唱片]]），并超过别的专辑在榜单上长久保持高位，打破了自1985年来的记录；专辑在全球销量超过3,100万。《21》也成功地使愛黛兒获得了《[[吉尼斯世界纪录大全|吉尼斯世界纪录大全]]》的无数认证。愛黛兒是[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]历史上第一位作为主唱同时拥有三首进入前十位的单曲的女歌手，也是历史上第一位同时在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上拥有两张进入前五位的专辑及两支单曲同时在公告牌百强单曲榜上位于前五位的女歌手，《21》是英国和美國专辑排行榜历史上由独唱歌手占据第一名排行最久的一张专辑。

2012年，愛黛兒尔为电影《[[007：大破天幕杀机|007：天降危機]]》合创并演唱了同名歌曲《[[天幕杀机_(歌曲)|天降危機]]》，这首歌曲获得了一项[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|奥斯卡奖]]、一项{{Le|格莱美奖最佳影视媒体作品歌曲|Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media|格莱美奖}}、一项[[金球奖最佳原創歌曲|金球獎]]以及[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]的“全英年度歌曲”獎項。在三年的休息之後，2015年，愛黛兒發行了她的第三張錄音室專輯《[[25_(愛黛兒專輯)|25]]》，这張專輯成为了年度销量最佳的專輯，在英國打破了{{Le|最暢銷專輯列表|Lists of fastest-selling albums|首周销量纪录}}。《25》是她第二张获得鑽石销量认证的專輯，也使她赢得了包括她的第二个“年度专辑”在内的[[第59届格莱美奖|五项格莱美奖]]及[[2016年全英音樂獎|四项全英音乐奖]]。专辑首支单曲《[[你好_(阿黛尔歌曲)|你好]]》成为美国第一支首周内数字销量超过百万的歌曲。她的第三次巡回演出{{Le|愛黛兒现场2016|Adele Live 2016}}在欧洲、北美及大洋洲展开，并于2017年中在[[温布利球场|温布利球场]]举行了最后演出。

2011年、2012年及2016年，愛黛兒被《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》评為年度藝人<ref name="KCaulfield">{{Cite web |author=Keith Caulfield |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/42119/the-year-in-pop-adele-makes-history |title=The Year in Pop: Adele Makes History |publisher=Billboard.com |date=2011-12-09 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523063026/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/42119/the-year-in-pop-adele-makes-history |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ArtistofYear">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-20747039 "Adele named Billboard top artist of 2012"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-20747039 |date=20130314045003 }}. BBC News. Retrieved 17 December 2012</ref>。2012年，愛黛兒被[[VH1|VH1]]评选为“樂壇最偉大的女性”第五位<ref name="VH1 100"/>。2012年及2016年，美國雜誌《[[时代_(杂志)|時代周刊]]》评选愛黛兒为「世界上最有影響力的人」之一<ref name="Time 100"/>。愛黛兒的唱片銷量總數超過1億張，是[[畅销音乐艺人列表|史上最畅销的藝人]]之一<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife-news/tickets-see-adele-birmingham-up-11009968|title=Tickets to see Adele in Birmingham up for sale for jaw-dropping £1,300 EACH|last=Bentley|first=David|date=2016-05-10|work={{tsl|en|Birmingham Mail||The Birmingham Mail}}|accessdate=2016-03-11|archive-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030032344/http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife-news/tickets-see-adele-birmingham-up-11009968|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早期生活 ==
愛黛兒·劳丽·布鲁·阿德金斯，1988年5月5日出生於英國[[倫敦|倫敦]][[埃德蒙頓_(倫敦)|埃德蒙頓]]北米德爾塞克斯大學醫院。她的父親馬克·伊凡斯（Mark Evans），為[[威爾斯人|威爾斯人]]；而母親潘妮·亞金斯（Penny Adkins），為英格蘭人。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Dreams|title=Someone Like Adele|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5Dr_AgAAQBAJ&pg=PT8&dq=adele+born+london+hospital&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjG3fqGgtH1AhUIG6YKHbL_DQYQ6AF6BAgLEAI#v=onepage&q=adele%20born%20london%20hospital&f=false|publisher=Omnibus Press|date=2012-03-13|isbn=978-0-85712-992-5|language=en|first=Caroline|last=Sanderson|access-date=2022-01-27|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127054130/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5Dr_AgAAQBAJ&pg=PT8&dq=adele+born+london+hospital&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjG3fqGgtH1AhUIG6YKHbL_DQYQ6AF6BAgLEAI#v=onepage&q=adele%20born%20london%20hospital&f=false}}</ref>當愛黛兒2歲的時候，她的父親離家出走，留下她和當時只有20歲的母親，之後由她的母親獨力撫養<ref>{{Cite web|last=Haines |first=Chris |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2012/02/18/adele-s-welsh-father-mark-evans-reveals-his-heartache-over-letting-down-six-time-grammy-awards-winner-91466-30356409/ |title=Adele's Welsh father Mark Evans reveals his heartache over 'letting down' six-time Grammy Awards winner – Wales News – News |publisher=WalesOnline |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29}}</ref>，因此，愛黛兒至今仍未原諒他的父親<ref name=VanMeter>{{Cite web |last=Van |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.vogue.com/magazine/article/adele-one-and-only/ |title=Adele: One and Only – Magazine |publisher=Vogue |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214164937/https://www.vogue.com/magazine/article/adele-one-and-only |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008|title=Mad about the girl|work=The Guardian|location=UK|date=2008-01-27|accessdate=2010-04-23|first=Sylvia|last=Patterson|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120110927/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008|archivedate=2010-11-20|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1135182/Adele-I-say-I-power-I-do.html |title=Adele: 'I have all the say; I have power over everything I do' | Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2009-02-13 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322203304/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1135182/Adele-I-say-I-power-I-do.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，她還有一個同父異母的弟弟，叫卡梅倫，現時跟她父親一起生活<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/822595/Adele-Adkins-Teen-singer-Unfazed-by-Brit-pressure.html |title=Adele Adkins | Teen singer | Unfazed by Brit pressure |publisher=The Sun |date=2008-02-20 |accessdate=2013-06-16 |archive-date=2013-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209070440/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/822595/Adele-Adkins-Teen-singer-Unfazed-by-Brit-pressure.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

愛黛兒自4歲起，便開始學習唱歌，並聲稱自己著迷於聲樂<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/entertainment/bal-li.music15jan15002019,0,4031087.story|title=Grammy-nominated Adele taking fame in stride|work=The Baltimore Sun|date=2009-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120720085255/http://www.baltimoresun.com/entertainment/bal-li.music15jan15002019,0,4031087.story|archivedate=2012-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.expressnightout.com/content/2009/01/singing_stronger_every_day_adele_stays_g.php | title=Singing Stronger Every Day: Adele | work=Express Night Out | date=2009-01-15 | agency=Washington Post | accessdate=2012-06-22 | author=Otiji, Adaora | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20110710212346/http://www.expressnightout.com/content/2009/01/singing_stronger_every_day_adele_stays_g.php | archivedate=2011-07-10 }}</ref>。她自認[[辣妹合唱團|辣妹合唱團]]對自己有很大的影響力，使她鍾愛於音樂，並曾說：「是她們成就了今天的我。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Walker|first=Marie|title=Adele: I Love the Spice Girls!|url=http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/517690/adele-i-love-the-spice-girls/1/|publisher=Now Magazine|accessdate=2011-03-06|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426182817/http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/517690/adele-i-love-the-spice-girls/1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>」。當她還是少女時，就曾在晚宴中模仿了辣妹合唱團<ref name=growingup>{{Cite web|url=http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/music/37642734.html?elr=KArksD:aDyaEP:kD:aUg:oaEQDUiD3aPc:_Yyc:aUU|title=Chasing Adele|work=Minneapolis Star Tribune|accessdate=2009-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130122142/http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/music/37642734.html?elr=KArksD%3AaDyaEP%3AkD%3AaUg%3AoaEQDUiD3aPc%3A_Yyc%3AaUU|archivedate=2011-11-30}}</ref>。另外，愛黛兒曾為了模仿英國的[[節奏藍調|節奏藍調]]暨當代城市歌手{{Link-en|賈布莉爾|Gabrielle (singer)}}，讓她媽媽為自己做了一個鑲有小亮片的眼罩，但後來愛黛兒表示，回想那段回憶令她十分尷尬<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3672957/Adele-young-soul-rebel.html |title=Adele: young soul rebel |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=UK |date=2008-04-25 |first=Stuart |last=Husband |accessdate=2010-04-23 |archive-date=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528062311/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3672957/Adele-young-soul-rebel.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在9歲時，她跟身為傢俱製造及成人學習活動籌辦者的母親移居到了[[布萊頓|布萊頓]]<ref>{{Cite news |author=Sylvia Patterson |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008 |title=Interview: Adele Atkins, singer |work=The Observer |location=UK |accessdate=2011-05-08 |date=2008-01-27 |archive-date=2010-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120110927/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Rollings">{{Cite news |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/3473210/The-truth-behind-Adeles-struggle-to-stardom.html |title=Teenage mum, cramped flats and truancy... the truth behind Adele's brave struggle to stardom |work=The Sun |location=UK |date=2011-03-17 |first=Grant |last=Rollings |accessdate=2011-11-28 |archive-date=2011-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124205503/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/3473210/The-truth-behind-Adeles-struggle-to-stardom.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2年後，她跟隨母親搬回倫敦。她們首先住在[[布里克斯頓|布里克斯頓]]<ref name="Rollings"/>，然後再搬到位於倫敦南部的[[西諾伍德區|西諾伍德區]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article3099702.ece|title=Adele-ation starts here |work=The Times |location=London  | first=Sophie|last=Heawood|date=2007-12-28}}</ref>—西諾伍德區曲是她創造的第一首單曲的主題，名為《{{Link-en|故鄉榮耀|Hometown Glory}}》，當時她僅得16歲<ref name=AmyWho>{{Cite news | url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/story/2009/01/30/ST2009013003292.html | title=Amy Who? Now, Adele's the One With the Buzz Washington Post 1 February 2009 | work=The Washington Post | first=Melinda | last=Newman | accessdate=2010-04-23 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629024345/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/story/2009/01/30/ST2009013003292.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。搬到倫敦南部後，愛黛兒對[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]歌手如[[艾莉婭|艾莉婭]]、[[天命真女|天命真女]]和[[瑪麗·布萊姬|瑪麗·布萊姬]]大感興趣<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bluesandsoul.com/feature/302/the_futures_looking_rosie_for_adele/ |title=ADELE: Up close and personal |publisher=Bluesandsoul.com |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708074331/http://www.bluesandsoul.com/feature/302/the_futures_looking_rosie_for_adele/ |archivedate=2011-07-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

愛黛兒曾說過，她最深刻的一次表演，就是當她在[[O2布里克斯頓學院|O2布里克斯頓學院]]觀賞歌手[[粉红佳人|紅粉佳人]]的表演，這大大改變了她對未來的人生，「那時聽的歌是《Missundaztood》，我記得當時我約13、14歲，那次是我第一次聽現場表演……我記得那種感覺就像是困在[[風洞|風洞]]裡一樣，她的聲音就這麼使我沉迷在其中，不能自拔。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spinner.com/2010/12/23/adele-defining-moments/ |title=Adele – Defining Moments |publisher=Spinner |date=2010-12-23 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130104194523/http://www.spinner.com/2010/12/23/adele-defining-moments/ |archivedate=2013-01-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://socialitelife.com/adele-says-hearing-pink-sing-changed-her-life-12-2010 |title=Adele Says Hearing Pink Sing Changed Her Life |publisher=Socialite Life |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120712132830/http://socialitelife.com/adele-says-hearing-pink-sing-changed-her-life-12-2010 |archivedate=2012-07-12 }}</ref> 」

當愛黛兒在14歲時，她在當地唱片行的[[爵士樂|爵士樂]]區無意中發現[[藍調|藍調]]歌手[[伊特·珍|伊特·珍]]和「爵士樂第一夫人」[[艾拉·費茲潔拉|艾拉·費茲潔拉]]的專輯，並被她們專輯封面的外觀所震撼<ref name=AmyWho/>。她稱「自己自那時開始，每晚都要聽一小時伊特·珍的專輯」。她深受她們以及美國爵士樂影響，並在過程中「找到了屬於自己的聲音」<ref name=AmyWho/>，並形容自己的音樂風格為「令人心碎的靈魂」（Heartbroken Soul）。

她在2006年於[[克羅伊登區|克羅伊登區]]的{{Link-en|全英演藝學校|BRIT School}}<ref name="Feet">{{Cite news| first=Jacqui| last=Swift| title=I will Always Keep Feet on Ground| date=2008-01-18| work=The Sun| url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/sftw/article698887.ece| accessdate=2008-02-12| location=London| archive-date=2012-10-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023134641/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/sftw/article698887.ece| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Soul">{{Cite news| first=Ian| last=Youngs| title=Soul singers top new talent list| publisher=BBC News| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7169307.stm| date=2008-01-04| accessdate=2010-01-01| archive-date=2009-02-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216150802/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7169307.stm| dead-url=no}}</ref>畢業，在那裡一同畢業同學的還有：[[里歐娜·路易斯|里歐娜·路易斯]]和[[潔西J|潔西J]]<ref name="nicole" /><ref name="collis">Collis, Clark (19 December 2008), "Spotlight on... Adele". ''Entertainment Weekly''. (1026):62</ref>。她謙虛地稱自己現時所擁有的才華都要歸功於學校的悉心指導<ref name="BlogCriticsInterview" />。由於她身為學生時，對[[A&R|培訓藝人]]（A&R）有濃厚的興趣，所以現時身為歌手的她希望能幫助其他人，推動的他們的音樂事業<ref name="nicole" />。

== 演唱生涯 ==
===2006－2010年：事業開始及《19》 ===
[[File:Adele.jpg|thumb]]
自畢業後4個月，愛黛兒於網上藝術雜誌 PlatformsMagazine.com 的第4期發布了兩首歌<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.platformsmagazine.com/4/contents.htm |title=Platform 04 |publisher=Platformsmagazine.com |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722121600/http://www.platformsmagazine.com/4/contents.htm |archivedate=2011-07-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。她為課堂項目錄製了三首歌曲樣本，然後交給朋友<ref name=nicole/>，就是後來上傳至[[Myspace|MySpace]]的歌曲。那些歌曲成功獲得廣大迴響，引來唱片公司[[XL唱片|XL唱片]]對愛黛兒的注意。他們主動致電<ref name=collis/>，當時她半信半疑這個機會是否真的，因為她認識的唱片公司只有[[維京唱片|維京唱片]]一家，於是她帶著一位朋友一起參與會面<ref name=collis/><ref name=AdeleBillboard>{{Cite web|url=http://link.brightcove.com/services/link/bcpid1184417216/bctid1612733606 |title=Billboard presents: Adele |publisher=Link.brightcove.com |accessdate=2011-08-18}}</ref>。

2006年6月，XL唱片的尼克·胡吉特（Nick Huggett）將愛黛兒推薦給九月經紀公司 （September Management）的喬納森·迪金斯（Jonathan Dickins），於是喬納森·迪金斯就成為她的官方代表<ref name="hitquarters.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/opar/intrview_Jonathan_Dickins_Interview.html |title=Interview with Jonathan Dickins |publisher={{tsl|en|HitQuarters||HitQuarters}} |date=2008-07-14 |accessdate=2011-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705064832/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2Fopar%2Fintrview_Jonathan_Dickins_Interview.html |archive-date=2015-07-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。九月經紀當時也是{{Link-en|傑米·T|Jamie T}}的經紀公司，這對愛黛兒形成極大誘因，畢竟她是這位英國創作歌手的大歌迷。2006年9月，尼克·胡吉特便跟愛黛兒簽約<ref name="hitquarters.com"/>。愛黛兒第一項工作是為{{Link-en|傑克·佩納特|Jack Peñate}}首張專輯的歌《My Yvonne》提供聲音。就在這段期間，她與製作人{{Link-en|吉姆·阿比斯|Jim Abbiss}}首次見面，後者就是她的首張專輯《19》及第二張專輯《21》製作人<ref name=penate>{{Cite news |last=Jones |first=Damian |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7986334.stm |title=Peñate collaborates with Adele |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-04-06 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2012-09-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AM7qmbqc?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7986334.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而她的突破性歌曲《故鄉之頌》（Hometown Glory）在2007年10月發布<ref name="hitquarters.com"/>。2007年，她出席在[[伊斯靈頓|伊斯靈頓]]聯合教堂舉行的《小噪音演奏會》，支持{{Link-en|威爾·楊|Will Young}}為{{Link-en|學習障礙組織|MENCAP}}的慈善演唱會。此外，她還到各處進行個人巡迴演出。

[[File:Adele_2009.jpg|thumb]]
2008年，愛黛兒得到[[戴米恩·莱斯|戴米恩·莱斯]]的支持下進行現場演唱，並成為了報章標題<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/hi/music/newsid_7724000/7724590.stm |title=Q&A: Adele's charity acoustic set BBC Radio 1 |date=2008-11-12 |accessdate=2010-01-01 |publisher=BBC News |archive-date=2012-07-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120715023746/http://news.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/hi/music/newsid_7724000/7724590.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://itn.co.uk/news/ea18cad798e196a3a8e02d93db6fca64.html|title=Adele hits the big time |publisher=ITN |date=2008-11-12}}{{dead link|date=August 2011}}</ref>。隨後她成為第一位獲得[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]評審團獎，她被預期為在[[英国广播公司|BBC]]票選中突破演出首選人物，成為《2008好聲音》<ref>{{Cite news |last=Youngs |first=Ian |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7168252.stm |title=Entertainment | Sound of 2008: Adele |publisher=BBC News |date=2008-01-04 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2009-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090107084258/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7168252.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1315959/adele-wins-brits-critics-choice-award |title=Adele Wins Brits Critics Choice Award |publisher=Billboard.com |date=2009-09-14 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523052702/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1315959/adele-wins-brits-critics-choice-award |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[19_(專輯)|19]]》是以愛黛兒當時的年齡命名，她寫了很多歌曲，入選《英國排行榜》第一位。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》及《[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]》現代音樂百科全書命名《19》為「重要的藍眼睛靈魂」的記錄<ref name="BlueEyedSoul">{{Cite news | url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article5597699.ece | title=Blue-eyed soul: Encyclopedia of Modern Music The Times | location=London | date=2009-02-01 | accessdate=2010-04-23 | first=Dan | last=Cairns | archive-date=2011-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616203103/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article5597699.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年1月14日，愛黛兒提前發布了她的第二首單曲《{{Link-en|Chasing Pavements}}》，兩個星期後，《19》於2008年1月28日發行了。這首歌登上英國榜第二位的佳績，更停留於榜上四個星期<ref name="nme.com">{{Cite news| title=This Week's Releases: 21 January 2008| work=NME| location=UK| url=http://www.nme.com/news/lightspeed-champion/33736| date=2008-01-21| accessdate=2013-08-09| archive-date=2014-01-31| archive-url=https://archive.today/20140131101252/http://www.nme.com/news/lightspeed-champion/33736| dead-url=no}}</ref>。她更因為《19》被提名到[[水星音樂獎|水星音樂獎]]<ref>{{Cite web |author=Jade Wright |url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/views/liverpool-columnists/echo-columnists/2008/07/23/puppets-tipped-for-music-prize-100252-21388721/ |title=Views & Blogs—Columnists—Echo columnists—Last Shadow Puppets tipped for Nationwide Mercury music prize |publisher=Liverpool Echo |date=2008-07-23 |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-date=2012-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013055214/http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/views/liverpool-columnists/echo-columnists/2008/07/23/puppets-tipped-for-music-prize-100252-21388721/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她還在{{Link-en|城市音樂獎|Urban Music Awards}}中贏得「最佳爵士演繹獎」<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://urbanmusicawards.net/2011/07/a-6/ | title=Winners for 6th Annual Urban Music Awards 2008 Announced | publisher=Urban Music Awards | date=2008-11-16 | accessdate=2012-06-22 | archive-date=2012-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120202074304/http://urbanmusicawards.net/2011/07/a-6/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她的突破演出獲{{Link-en|Q獎|Q Awards}}的提名<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2008/09/03/duffy-nominated-for-q-awards-double-91466-21662021|title=Duffy nominated for Q awards double Wales Online|date=2008-09-03|accessdate=2013-08-09|archive-date=2008-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207032644/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2008/09/03/duffy-nominated-for-q-awards-double-91466-21662021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，及在《黑色音樂原產地》中被提名為「英國最佳女性」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gigwise.com/news/45979/estelle-and-leona-lewis-lead-2008-mobo-nominations |title=Estelle And Leona Lewis Lead 2008 Mobo Nominations |publisher=Gigwise |date=2008-09-11 |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-date=2015-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413105420/http://www.gigwise.com/news/45979/estelle-and-leona-lewis-lead-2008-mobo-nominations |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2008年3月，愛黛兒跟XL唱片與[[哥倫比亞唱片|哥倫比亞唱片]]簽署一項協議，為進軍美國市場進發<ref name="Columbia">{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1046129/adele-inks-us-deal-with-columbia |title=Adele Inks U.S. Deal With Columbia |work=Billboard |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523074918/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1046129/adele-inks-us-deal-with-columbia |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然後她於同月在[[北美|北美]]開始了一個很短的巡迴表演<ref name="Columbia"/>，並在6月在美國發行她的專輯《19》<ref name="BlogCriticsInterview" />。《告示榜雜誌》指，愛黛兒有真正的潛質成為她這一代中最受專敬及最鼓舞人心的國際藝人<ref name="Billboard2008">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=_hIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA50&lpg=PA50&dq=Billboard.+10+May+2008+-+Adele+truly+has+potential+to+become+among+the+most+respected+and+inspiring+international+artists+of+her+generation&source=bl&ots=TrNJpIPPfd&sig=CaiTFt73BurvflvISR8JHF8aDDc&hl=en&sa=X&ei=c29yT7nkKcTc8gOA8NF0&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Billboard – Google Books |publisher=Books.google.com |date=2008-06-07 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528130452/http://books.google.com/books?id=_hIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA50&lpg=PA50&dq=Billboard.+10+May+2008+-+Adele+truly+has+potential+to+become+among+the+most+respected+and+inspiring+international+artists+of+her+generation&source=bl&ots=TrNJpIPPfd&sig=CaiTFt73BurvflvISR8JHF8aDDc&hl=en&sa=X&ei=c29yT7nkKcTc8gOA8NF0&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《{{Link-en|與愛黛兒的黃昏|An Evening with Adele}}》世界巡迴演唱會於2008年5月開始，2009年6月結束。她後來取消了美國的巡迴，跟她的前男友在一起，她在2009年6月的《[[尼龍雜誌|尼龍雜誌]]》中說：「我是喝得太多，這是我跟這個男孩的關係，我不能承受得到失去他，所以我就像是『好吧，沒問題，然後我就取消自己的事...』我也不敢相信我會這樣做，它似乎也蠻忘恩負義的」。2008年10月中，愛黛兒嘗試打進美國市場的計劃似乎已經失敗了<ref name=MELISSARUGGIER>{{Cite web|url=http://www.inrich.com/cva/ric/entertainment.apx.-content-articles-RTD-2008-10-23-0002.html|title=The Richmond Times Dispatch | date=2008-10-23}}{{dead link|date=August 2011}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.boston.com/ae/celebrity/articles/2009/01/12/19_going_on_superstar/ | title='19' going on superstar | work=The Boston Globe | first=James | last=Reed | date=2009-01-12 | accessdate=2013-08-09 | archive-date=2009-05-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505084013/http://www.boston.com/ae/celebrity/articles/2009/01/12/19_going_on_superstar/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨後她在2008年10月18日的《[[周末夜现场|周末夜现场]]》，該節目贏得14年來最高收視率，有17,000,000人收看。節目中她演唱《{{Link-en|Chasing Pavements|Chasing Pavements}}》和《{{Link-en|Cold Shoulder (愛黛兒歌曲)|Cold Shoulder (Adele song)|Cold Shoulder}}》<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://tv.nytimes.com/episode/4924446/Saturday-Night-Live/overview|title=Saturday Night Live Season 34 Josh Brolin/Adele|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2011-05-08|archive-date=2012-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217015323/http://tv.nytimes.com/episode/4924446/Saturday-Night-Live/overview|dead-url=no}}</ref>，翌日《19》榮登iTunes榜第五位，而《Chasing Pavements》升到Amazon.com的首25位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/backstage-pass-1.811987/adele-enjoys-an-snl-bump-1.832659|title=Adele enjoys an "SNL" bump|work=Newsday|date=2008-10-20|accessdate=2013-08-09|archive-date=2012-06-29|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120629202247/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/backstage-pass-1.811987/adele-enjoys-an-snl-bump-1.832659|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《19》最終在《[[告示榜200|告示榜200]]》中排名第11，比之前一周跳升35位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1043648/acdc-debuts-at-no-1-with-784000|title=AC/DC Debuts At No. 1 With 784,000|work=Billboard|date=2008-10-29|accessdate=2013-08-09|archive-date=2013-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329093034/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1043648/acdc-debuts-at-no-1-with-784000|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年11月，愛黛兒自離開母親的屋後，搬到[[諾丁山|諾丁山]]居住，此舉令她戒酒<ref name=Cancel2008>{{Cite web |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/adele-explains-2008-booze-love-meltdown_1105845 |title=Adele Explains Booze & Love Meltdown |date=2009-06-08 |publisher=Contactmusic |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2009-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090703123730/http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/adele-explains-2008-booze-love-meltdown_1105845 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她的專輯於2009年2月獲得[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]金唱片的認證<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?news_month_filter=&news_year_filter=&resultpage=&id=DDB9AF12-8F76-11DE-4FF2-E1988D17AA66 |title=Perry's Platinum Pucker |date=2009-03-23 |publisher=RIAA |accessdate=2011-05-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629041254/http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?news_month_filter=&news_year_filter=&resultpage=&id=DDB9AF12-8F76-11DE-4FF2-E1988D17AA66 |archivedate=2011-06-29 }}</ref>。2009年7月，《19》已在全球售出2,000,000張<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/a166444/adele-puts-career-on-hold-for-dog.html |title=Adele 'puts career on hold for dog |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2009-07-21 |accessdate=2011-05-08}}</ref>。2009年2月8日[[第51屆葛萊美獎|第51屆葛萊美獎]]上，愛黛兒榮獲「最佳新人」和「最佳流行女歌手」兩項獎，熱門歌曲《Chasing Pavements》亦獲得「年度唱片」和「年度歌曲」的提名肯定，她還獲得2009年全英音樂獎最佳英國女藝人、最佳英國單曲和英國突破藝人三項提名。

2010年1月31日[[第52屆葛萊美獎|第52屆葛萊美獎]]上，愛黛兒以歌曲《Hometown Glory》獲得「最佳流行女歌手」提名的肯定<ref>{{Cite press_release | url=http://www.cbspressexpress.com/cbs-radio/releases/print?id=27520 | title=TWO-TIME GRAMMY AWARD WINNER ADELE TO PERFORM ON CBS INTERACTIVE MUSIC GROUP'S "LIVE ON LETTERMAN" WEBCAST SERIES | publisher=CBS | accessdate=2012-06-22 | archive-date=2013-10-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022141735/http://www.cbspressexpress.com/cbs-radio/releases/print?id=27520 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在4月，自從[[莉娜·邁耶-蘭德魯特|莉娜·邁耶-蘭德魯特]]在才藝表演大賽{{Link-en|我們的奧斯陸星|Unser Star für Oslo}}中演繹愛黛兒的歌曲《[[19_(阿黛尔专辑)|My Same]]》，及《[[歐洲歌唱大賽2010|歐洲歌唱大賽2010]]》後，歌曲打進《[[德國單曲榜|德國單曲榜]]》<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=http://esctoday.com/news/read/14983|title=Live: First heat in Germany|last=Klier|first=Marcus|date=2010-02-02|work=ESCToday|accessdate=2011-02-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208230815/http://www.esctoday.com/news/read/14983|archivedate=2010-02-08}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{de icon}}{{Cite web|url=http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/title/Adele/My+Same/single|title=Musicline.de – Chartverfolgung – Adele – My Same|date=2010-02-21|publisher=[[GfK娱乐榜单|Media Control Charts]]|accessdate=2011-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719065231/http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/title/Adele/My+Same/single|archive-date=2011-07-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref> <ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/><ref name="#3">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nme.com/news/oasis/53223 |title=Oasis, Radiohead and Adele set for chart re-entries thanks to 'The X Factor'? |work=NME |location=UK |date=2010-09-29 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2011-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628225841/http://www.nme.com/news/oasis/53223 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《CMT年度藝人》特別節目中，愛黛兒與{{Link-en|達留斯·路克|Darius Rucker}}一起在當中演唱了[[懷舊女郎|懷舊女郎]]的《{{tsl|en|Need You Now (Lady Antebellum song)|Need You Now (歌曲)|Need You Now}}》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kncifm.radio.com/2011/01/16/darius-rucker-and-adele-cover-lady-antebellums-need-you-now/ |title=Adele and Darius Rucker perform Need You Now on CMT Artists of the Year |publisher=Kncifm.radio.com |date=2011-01-16 |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110217151616/http://kncifm.radio.com/2011/01/16/darius-rucker-and-adele-cover-lady-antebellums-need-you-now/ |archive-date=2011-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，這個表演使他們後來被考慮提名到{{Link-en|CMT音樂頒獎|CMT Music Awards}}<ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/><ref>{{Cite journal|url=http://www.cmt.com/news/country-music/1662725/2011-cmt-music-awards-nominees-revealed.jhtml|title=2011 CMT Music Awards Nominees Revealed|year=2011|accessdate=2011-05-07|publisher=[[CMT|CMT]]|journal=|archive-date=2013-01-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Du5PfgN8?url=http://www.cmt.com/news/country-music/1662725/2011-cmt-music-awards-nominees-revealed.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月下旬，當愛黛兒在《[[英國版X音素|英國版X音素]]》節目中以自己的方法來演繹[[巴布·狄倫|巴布·狄倫]]的《{{Link-en|Make You Feel My Love|Make You Feel My Love}}》，使這首歌重新打進《[[英國單曲榜|英國單曲榜]]》第4位<ref name="#3"/>。

===2011－2012年：《21》 ===
愛黛兒於2011年1月24日在英國推出她的第二張錄音室專輯《[[21_(專輯)|21]]》，在美國於2011年2月22日推出<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/952006/adele-to-release-21-sophomore-album-in-february |title=Adele to Release '21' Sophomore Album in February Billboard 2 November 2010 |work=Billboard |date=2009-09-14 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2013-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524173207/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/952006/adele-to-release-21-sophomore-album-in-february |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SecondAlbum">{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a285526/adele-announces-second-album-details.html|title=Adele announces second album details|last=Levine|first=Nick|date=2010-11-02|publisher=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|accessdate=2010-11-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105024406/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a285526/adele-announces-second-album-details.html|archivedate=2010年11月5日|deadurl=no}}</ref>。她說這張專輯的靈感是來自跟前伴侶分開<ref name=VanMeter/>。專輯中的音樂被形容為古典及現代的[[鄉村音樂|鄉村音樂]]和{{Link-en|草根音樂|Roots revival}}。她第一張專輯的音樂轉變，是來自當愛黛兒遊覽美國南部時，她的旅遊車司機正播放[[纳什维尔|納許維爾]]的現代音樂，而標題反映了她在過去兩年的成長與經歷<ref name="SecondAlbum"/>。她在《[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]]》中說：「這是對我來說真的很興奮的，因為我沒接觸過這種音樂<ref name=Spin21>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spin.com/articles/adele-new-record-quite-different |title=Adele: New Record is 'Quite Different' |work=Spin Magazine |date=2010-11-02 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archive-date=2015-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511211143/http://www.spin.com/articles/adele-new-record-quite-different |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

《21》在超過30個國家流行榜中登上第一位，包括英國及美國<ref name="Independent2012">{{Cite news |author=Nick Clark |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/adele-surges-past-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-on-inexorable-voyage-to-stardom-7578154.html |title=Adele surges past The Dark Side of the Moon on inexorable voyage to stardom – News – Music |publisher=The Independent |date=2012-03-20 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615174304/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/adele-surges-past-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-on-inexorable-voyage-to-stardom-7578154.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chartstats.com/release.php?release=49903 |title=ChartArchive – Adele – 21 |publisher=Chartstats.com |date=2012-06-25 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120629202507/http://www.chartstats.com/release.php?release=49903 |archivedate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Kaufman |first=Gil |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1660010/lupe-fiasco-lasers-billboard.jhtml |title=Lupe Fiasco's Lasers Blasts To Top Of Billboard 200 |publisher=MTV |date=2011-03-16 |accessdate=2011-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514012938/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1660010/lupe-fiasco-lasers-billboard.jhtml |archivedate=2011-05-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在2011年2月15日的[[2011年全英音樂獎|2011年全英音樂獎]]中，《[[Someone_like_You_(愛黛兒歌曲)|Someone like You]]》有一個情感的表現，替這歌在英國推上榜首的位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/adele/259080-adele-number-1-single-album-someone-like-you-brits |title=Adele's 'Someone Like You' Tops UK Singles Chart | Adele | News | MTV UK |publisher=Mtv.co.uk |date=2011-02-21 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021095837/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/adele/259080-adele-number-1-single-album-someone-like-you-brits |dead-url=no }}</ref>。愛黛兒的第一張專輯《19》和第二張專輯《21》的《[[Rolling_in_the_Deep|Rolling in the Deep]]》及《Someone Like You》都在英國單曲榜上位列前5名位置，使她成為現存的藝人繼1964年[[披頭四|披頭四]]之後，同時有兩首歌同時在《官方單曲榜》及《官方專輯榜》上實現登上首五位，並保持5星期<ref>{{Cite web |author=Sean Michaels |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/feb/22/adele-matches-beatles-chart-success |title=Adele matches the Beatles in latest chart success |publisher=Guardian |date=2011-02-22 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2011-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219030800/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/feb/22/adele-matches-beatles-chart-success |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/3423559/Singer-Adele-makes-it-to-the-top-of-the-charts.html |title=Singer Adele makes it to the top of the charts |publisher=The Sun |date=2011-02-21 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023134746/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/3423559/Singer-Adele-makes-it-to-the-top-of-the-charts.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩首歌在多個地區的榜上位列第一，打破了多個銷售業績的紀錄。2011年5月，愛黛兒因為高稅收的一些關鍵陳述而引起一起小爭議<ref>{{Cite web |author=Jenna Good |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2001582/Adele-triggers-online-backlash-recent-comments-pay-tax.html |title=Adele triggers online backlash after her recent comments on how much she has to pay in tax |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2011-06-10 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2011-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110801064447/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2001582/Adele-triggers-online-backlash-recent-comments-pay-tax.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨著她在[[2011年MTV音樂錄像獎|2011年MTV音樂錄像獎]]上，《Someone Like You》的表現，使她的歌再次打進《[[告示牌百大單曲榜|告示牌百大單曲榜]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/467566/adeles-someone-like-you-soars-to-no-1-on-hot-100 |title=Adele's 'Someone Like You' Soars To No. 1 On Hot 100 |publisher=Billboard.com |date=2009-09-14 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2011-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110729050908/http://www.billboard.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年12月，《21》在英國銷售量超過375萬張，13個白金唱片，超越已故歌手[[艾美·懷恩豪斯|艾美·懷恩豪斯]]的《[[黑色會|Back to Black]]》，成為21世紀最暢銷的專輯<ref name=Jones>{{Cite web|last=Jones|first=Alan|title=Official Album Chart analysis: Olly Murs becomes 10th X-Factor No.1|url=http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1047728&c=1|work={{tsl|en|Music Week||Music Week}}|accessdate=2011-12-04|date=2011-12-04|archive-date=2012-01-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120118043506/http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1047728&c=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Adele's album is century's biggest|url=http://music.uk.msn.com/news/adeles-album-is-centurys-biggest|work=[[MSN|MSN.co.uk]]|accessdate=2011-12-05|date=2011-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108051251/http://music.uk.msn.com/news/adeles-album-is-centurys-biggest|archive-date=2012-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，使愛黛兒成為有史以來第一位在一年內賣出超過300萬張專輯<ref>{{Cite web |last=Smirke |first=Richard |url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/record-labels/adele-makes-u-k-chart-history-first-artist-1005340982.story |title=Adele Makes U.K. Chart History: First Artist To Sell 3 Million Albums In Same Year |publisher=Billboard.biz |date=2011-09-07 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-07-19 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120719102418/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/record-labels/adele-makes-u-k-chart-history-first-artist-1005340982.story |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | date = 2011-09-07 | url = http://www.officialcharts.com/press/adele-breaks-official-charts-history-with-3-million-album-sales/ | title = 07/09/2011 – Adele breaks Official Charts history with 3 million album sales | publisher = Official Charts Company | accessdate = 2012-06-22 | archive-date = 2012-06-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120628025959/http://www.officialcharts.com/press/adele-breaks-official-charts-history-with-3-million-album-sales/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在美國，《21》每周平均銷售是122.2萬張，銷售量達到560萬張，得到5項白金唱片，此外亦同時成為全球最暢銷大碟，全球銷售高達1600萬張。

《[[Set_Fire_to_the_Rain|Set Fire to the Rain]]》成為她第三支冠軍單曲入選《告示牌百大單曲榜》，使愛黛兒的《21》成為首個藝人的專輯保持在榜首位置，而同時擁有3首冠軍單曲在《告示牌榜單》中<ref name="CapitalFM">{{Cite web |url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/billboard-history/ |title=Adele Makes Billboard History After 'Set Fire To The Rain' Tops US Chart |publisher=Capital FM |date=2012-01-27 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-01-02 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130102032810/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/billboard-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

