為了宣傳新專輯，愛黛兒踏上她的《{{Link-en|愛黛兒巡迴演唱會|Adele Live}}》之旅，門票於北美售罊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.allheadlinenews.com/articles/7020819787?Adele%20Announces%20European%20Tour%20In%20Support%20Of%20%2221%22 |title=Adele Announces European Tour In Support Of "21" |author=Jones, Anthony |date=2010-12-15 |work={{tsl|en|All Headline News||All Headline News}} |accessdate=2011-02-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130132359/http://www.allheadlinenews.com/articles/7020819787?Adele%20Announces%20European%20Tour%20In%20Support%20Of%20%2221%22 |archivedate=2011-11-30 }}</ref>。2011年10月，愛黛兒因聲帶出血，被迫取消兩場巡迴演唱。同時她發表了聲明，指她需要休息一段長時間，避免她的聲音永久受損<ref>{{Cite web |author=By Benjy Eisen |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-cancels-u-s-tour-due-to-illness-20111004 |title=Adele Cancels U.S. Tour Due to Illness | Music News |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120712053907/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-cancels-u-s-tour-due-to-illness-20111004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期後她在11月的首個星期於[[波士頓|波士頓]]的[[麻省總醫院|麻省總醫院]]接受雷射顯微外科手術<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/throat-operation-was-success/ |title=Adele: "Throat Operation Was A Success" |publisher=Capital FM |date=2011-11-14 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621110829/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/throat-operation-was-success/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boston.cbslocal.com/2011/11/07/mgh-adele-to-make-full-recovery-after-vocal-surgery/ |title=MGH: Adele To Make Full Recovery After Vocal Surgery « CBS Boston |publisher=Boston.cbslocal.com |date=2011-11-07 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312132550/http://boston.cbslocal.com/2011/11/07/mgh-adele-to-make-full-recovery-after-vocal-surgery/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的巡迴演唱會錄音《{{Link-en|皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳演唱會 (愛黛兒影片)|Live at the Royal Albert Hall (Adele video)|皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳演唱會}}》在2011年11月發布，開售時售出9.6萬張，是計算一星期內最高音樂DVD，成為4年內最暢銷的音樂DVD<ref>{{Cite web |author= |url=http://abcnewsradioonline.com/music-news/2011/12/8/adeles-new-dvd-live-at-the-royal-albert-hall-is-best-selling.html |title=Adele's New DVD "Live at the Royal Albert Hall" Is Best-Selling Music Video of 2011 – Music News – ABC News Radio |publisher=Abcnewsradioonline.com |date=2011-12-08 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729060253/http://abcnewsradioonline.com/music-news/2011/12/8/adeles-new-dvd-live-at-the-royal-albert-hall-is-best-selling.html |archivedate=2013-07-29 }}</ref>。愛黛兒是在{{Link-en|世界專輯榜|Nielsen SoundScan}}的歷來首位藝人得到該年的成績：一年一張專輯 (《[[21_(專輯)|21]]》)、榜首單曲 (《Rolling in the Deep》)，以及榜首音樂錄像<ref name=yahoomusic>{{Cite web|url= http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-dec-4-2011-albums-headed-triple-164834637.html|title= Week Ending Dec. 4, 2011. Albums: Headed For A Triple Crown|publisher= yahoo.com|accessdate= 2013-08-10|archive-date= 2012-01-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120109101932/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-dec-4-2011-albums-headed-triple-164834637.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。在11月20日的[[2011年全美音樂獎|2011年全美音樂獎]]，愛黛兒贏得3個獎項：最受歡迎流行/搖滾女歌手、最歡迎成年現代藝人，及最受歡迎流行/搖滾專輯《21》<ref name="AMA">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15815917 |title=BBC News – Adele and Taylor Swift rule at American Music Awards |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2011-11-21 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011000446/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15815917 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在12月9日，《告示牌榜單》命名愛黛兒為年度藝人、告示牌200大年度專輯《21》、告示牌百大年度單曲《Rolling in the Deep》，她成為成為有史以來的第一位女性囊括以上三個獎項<ref name="KCaulfield"/><ref>{{Cite web |last=Sinha |first=Piya |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/10/us-adele-billboard-idUSTRE7B81T320111210 |title=Adele makes Billboard history, named 2011 top artist |publisher=Reuters |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429105108/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/10/us-adele-billboard-idUSTRE7B81T320111210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在聲帶手術之後，愛黛兒於2012年2月14日的[[第54屆葛萊美獎|第54屆葛萊美獎]]典禮上復出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/16809108 |title=Newsbeat – Adele to make comeback at Grammys after throat surgery |publisher=BBC |date=2012-01-31 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120203063044/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/16809108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她得到六項提名並橫掃囊括六獎，分別為「年度製作」/《Rolling in the Deep》、「年度專輯」/《21》、「年度歌曲」/《Rolling in the Deep》、「最佳流行歌手」/《Someone Like You》、「最佳流行演唱專輯」/《21》與「最佳短篇音樂錄影帶」/《Rolling in the Deep》，使她繼[[碧昂絲·諾利斯|碧昂絲]]後，在葛萊美獎史上第二位女藝人於一晚內贏得多個獎項<ref>{{Cite web|title=Grammy Awards 2012: Adele wins six awards tying with Beyoncé for most trophies won in one night|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/music-news/9078334/Grammy-Awards-2012-Adele-wins-six-awards-tying-with-Beyonce-for-most-trophies-won-in-one-night.html|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2012-02-13|date=2012-02-13|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007065359/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/music-news/9078334/Grammy-Awards-2012-Adele-wins-six-awards-tying-with-Beyonce-for-most-trophies-won-in-one-night.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自格林美獎頒獎禮後，根據尼爾森音樂自1991年的跟蹤統計數據顯示，《21》的銷售數字上升，獲得單週最大銷售額<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/504474/adeles-21-earns-biggest-sales-gain-in-soundscan-history |title=Adele's '21' Earns Biggest Sales Gain In SoundScan History |publisher=Billboard.com |date=2009-09-14 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523030816/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/504474/adeles-21-earns-biggest-sales-gain-in-soundscan-history |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PostGrammyRecord">{{Cite web |last=Kaufman |first=Gil |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1679672/adele-breaks-record-sales-grammy.jhtml |title=Adele Breaks Record By Selling 730,000 After Grammys – Music, Celebrity, Artist News |publisher=MTV.com |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610090302/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1679672/adele-breaks-record-sales-grammy.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年1月，《21》在《告示牌200大專輯榜》中，追平了[[席琳·狄翁|席琳·狄翁]]的專輯《Let's Talk About Love》16周冠軍記錄。愛黛兒在2月21日的{{Link-en|2012年全英音樂獎|2012 BRIT Awards}}中獲得「最佳英國女獨唱藝人」及「年度英國專輯」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16533246 |title=BBC News – Brit Awards 2012: List of winners |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2012-02-21 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806234343/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16533246 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=By Matthew Perpetua |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-coldplay-lead-brit-award-nominations-20120112 |title=Adele, Coldplay Lead BRIT Award Nominations | Music News |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=2012-01-12 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714011842/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-coldplay-lead-brit-award-nominations-20120112 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《全英音樂獎》之後，《21》在非連續的21周內登上《英國專輯榜》榜首<ref name="PostBrits">{{Cite web |url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-overtakes-michael-jackson-in-all-time-biggest-selling-albums-chart907/ |title=Adele overtakes Michael Jackson in all-time biggest selling albums cha |publisher=Theofficialcharts.com |date=2012-02-28 |accessdate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720232152/http://www.bpi.co.uk/assets/files/top%2040%20albums.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-20 }}</ref>，專輯在英國售出450萬張，在全天候《[[英國暢銷專輯列表|英國暢銷專輯列表]]》中第四位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-overtakes-oasis-to-become-the-fourth-biggest-selling-album-of-all-time-1778/|title=Adele overtakes Oasis to become the fourth biggest selling album of all-time|date=2012-12-29|accessdate=2012-12-30|archive-date=2012-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120628163557/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-overtakes-oasis-to-become-the-fourth-biggest-selling-album-of-all-time-1778/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在10月，專輯在英國衝破480萬張大關，並在11月於美國衝破1000萬張<ref name="billboarddiamond">Keith Caulfield (27 Nov 2012). [http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473979/adeles-21-hits-10-million-in-us-sales "Adele's '21' Hits 10 Million in U.S. Sales"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473979/adeles-21-hits-10-million-in-us-sales |date=20130523074854 }}. Billboard. Retrieved 29 November 2012</ref><ref name=riaadiamond>{{Cite news|url=http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?content_selector=newsandviews&news_month_filter=11&news_year_filter=2012&id=EFB7CD0F-C057-0494-A4D0-90A5A385816E|title=RIAA – Adele Earns RIAA Diamond for "21"|date=2012-11-28|accessdate=2012-11-28|archive-date=2013-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104122852/http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?content_selector=newsandviews&news_month_filter=11&news_year_filter=2012&id=EFB7CD0F-C057-0494-A4D0-90A5A385816E|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Gein |first=Paul |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-extra-adele-tops-10-million-120255136.html#more-3511 |title=Chart Watch Extra: Adele Tops 10 Million |publisher=Yahoo |date=2012-11-28 |accessdate=2012-11-29 |archive-date=2012-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121201015503/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-extra-adele-tops-10-million-120255136.html#more-3511 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。愛黛兒是過去10年在美國唯一的藝人或樂隊於兩年內一張專輯獲得[[RIAA认证|RIAA鑽石認證]]<ref name=riaadiamond/>。截至年底，《21》的成功帶動了《19》的銷量，兩碟銷售合總共3000萬張，是自2004年[[亞瑟小子|亞瑟小子]]的暢銷大碟《[[愛的告白_(亞瑟小子專輯)|Confessions]]》2000萬張銷售後，七年以來最暢銷的專輯，是2010年代第一張破1000萬張大關的大碟，亦在《告示牌200大專輯榜》從第10位躍升至第4位，這是近代西方流行音樂史上極罕見的情況，被[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]形容為「自己唯一的對手」。愛黛兒的專輯《21》最終在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|美國告示牌專輯榜]]一共獲得24週冠軍，在英國專輯榜一共獲得23週冠軍。2012年4月3日，愛黛兒落實她的第三張專輯可能會花至少兩年的時間，她說：「我需要多一點時間和現場表演，我的第一張跟第二張專輯相隔兩年是很好的，所以它將會在相同時間。」她指自己將繼續寫關於自己的東西<ref name="MTV2012">Kaufman, Gil (3 April 2012) [http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682315/adele-new-single.jhtml "Adele To Release New Single This Year"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682315/adele-new-single.jhtml |date=20120405203851 }}. MTV. Retrieved 19 October 2012</ref>。2012年6月，愛黛兒在部落格上宣布懷孕的消息，她與男友Simon正期待他們第一個寶寶的來臨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.adele.tv/blogcache/i-ve-got-some-news/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904133419/http://www.adele.tv/blogcache/i-ve-got-some-news/ |archivedate=2013-09-04 }}</ref>。

2012年10月，愛黛兒已落實為第23齣《[[占士邦|占士邦]]電影》作曲及錄製主題曲《[[天幕杀机_(歌曲)|空降危機]]》<ref>"[http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/19785659 Adele confirms Skyfall Bond theme song] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121204163556/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/19785659 |date=2012-12-04 }}" BBC Newsbeat, retrieved 1 October 2012</ref><ref>"[http://www.itv.com/news/2012-10-01/adele-to-sing-theme-to-new-james-bond-film-skyfall/ Adele to sing theme to new James Bond film Skyfall] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itv.com/news/2012-10-01/adele-to-sing-theme-to-new-james-bond-film-skyfall/ |date=20180702180229 }}", ITV.com, retrieved 1 October 2012</ref>，《空降危機》一曲，是跟電影製片人{{Link-en|Paul Epworth|Paul Epworth}}共同編寫，於[[艾比路工作室|艾比路工作室]]錄製，並得到{{Link-en|J. A. C. Redford|J. A. C. Redford}}編制管弦樂<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/OfficialAdele/status/252762323884847104/photo/1|title=Skyfall sheet|publisher=Adele Official [[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002230158/http://twitter.com/OfficialAdele/status/252762323884847104/photo/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|title=SKYFALL OFFICIAL THEME SONG NEWS RELEASE TO COINCIDE WITH BOND'S 50TH ANNIVERSARY|publisher=007.com|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DxHNzaD5?url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。愛黛兒表示錄製此歌曲期間是「我生命中最自豪的時間之一<ref>[http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/4566290/Adele-tweets-score-for-Bond-film-Skyfall.html#ixzz284zoc4Mb "Adele: Recording Skyfall was one of the proudest moments of my life"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/4566290/Adele-tweets-score-for-Bond-film-Skyfall.html#ixzz284zoc4Mb |date=20130721113838 }}. The Sun. Retrieved 1 October 2012</ref>。」10月14日，《空降危機》在《英國單曲榜》上升到第二位，銷售量92,000張，其整體銷量為17.6萬張。《空降危機》在《[[告示牌熱門100單曲榜|告示牌熱門100單曲榜]]》中排第8，是她自首張專輯後第一支於首10位的歌，在美國發行的首3天共售出26.1萬張<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474715/adeles-skyfall-not-a-lock-for-uk-no-1 |title=Adele's 'Skyfall' Not a Lock for U.K. No. 1 |date=2012-10-10 |publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌 (雜誌)]] |accessdate=2012-10-10 |archive-date=2013-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209044730/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474715/adeles-skyfall-not-a-lock-for-uk-no-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這紀錄平了[[杜蘭杜蘭|杜蘭杜蘭]]的《{{Link-en|A View to a Kill (歌曲)|A View to a Kill (song)|A View to a Kill}}》作為《占士邦電影》的主題曲於《英國單曲榜》的位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/swedish-house-mafia-deny-adele-a-number-1-single-for-a-second-week-1642/ |title=Swedish House Mafia deny Adele a Number 1 single for a second week |date=2012-10-14 |publisher=[[官方榜单公司|The Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=2012-10-14 |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017011420/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/swedish-house-mafia-deny-adele-a-number-1-single-for-a-second-week-1642/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《空降危機》單曲已經在全球售出超過200萬張<ref>[http://news.sky.com/story/1018076/adele-sets-new-record-for-us-album-sales "Adele Sets New Record For US Album Sales"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1018076/adele-sets-new-record-for-us-album-sales |date=20141111193822 }}. Sky News. Retrieved 29 November 2012</ref>。2012年12月，《告示牌榜單》給予愛黛兒的獎項：《年度藝人》及《年度專輯：21》，使她成為第一位連續兩年同時獲得這兩個獎項的人<ref name="ArtistofYear"/>，並命名為最受歡迎女歌手<ref name="ArtistofYear"/>。《[[美聯社|美聯社]]》把愛黛兒命名為《2012年年度藝人》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481295/adele-named-ap-entertainer-of-the-year |title=Adele Named AP Entertainer of the Year |date=2012-12-20 |publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌 (雜誌)]] |accessdate=2012-12-28 |archive-date=2013-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208220954/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481295/adele-named-ap-entertainer-of-the-year |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年8月，《21》的銷售達2800萬張。《21》是21世紀第2張最賣座的專輯，[[布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯|布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯]]的《[[爱的再告白_(专辑)|爱的再告白 (专辑)]]》、[[諾拉·瓊絲|諾拉·瓊絲]]的《[[遠走高飛_(諾拉·瓊斯專輯)|遠走高飛]]》，僅次於[[披頭四|披頭四]]的精選專輯《[[1_(披头士专辑)|1]]》。

