在2013年1月，在報導指愛黛兒正籌備新專輯<ref>{{Cite news| url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Adele-working-on-new-album/tabid/418/articleID/282547/Default.aspx| work=3 News NZ| title=Adele ‘working on new album’| date=2012-01-10| access-date=2013-08-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729051435/http://www.3news.co.nz/Adele-working-on-new-album/tabid/418/articleID/282547/Default.aspx| archive-date=2013-07-29| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，後來當她考慮在下一張專輯唱甚麼歌曲時，她也確認正為下一張專輯努力<ref>NME: Adele says she'll record a new album when she 'has something to sing about' http://www.nme.com/news/adele/68983 {{Wayback|url=http://www.nme.com/news/adele/68983 |date=20131023060100 }}</ref>。2013年1月13日，愛黛兒憑《[[007：空降危機|007：空降危機]]》所演唱的電影主題曲《Skyfall》獲得[[第70屆金球獎|第70屆金球獎]]的「最佳原創歌曲獎」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/2013/01/winners-list/ |title=The 70th Annual Golden Globe Awards, Winners List |date=2013-01-14 |publisher=[[好莱坞外国记者协会|HFPA]] |accessdate=2013-01-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130414202011/http://www.goldenglobes.org/2013/01/winners-list/ |archivedate=2013-04-14 }}</ref>，並在2013年2月10日舉行的[[第55屆葛萊美獎|第55屆葛萊美獎]]上，愛黛兒在《皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳演唱會》現場版的《Set Fire To The Rain 》贏得「最佳流行歌手」殊榮<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1050358/grammys-adele-wins-best-pop-solo-performance|title=Grammys: Adele Wins Best Pop Solo Performance|publisher=Sky News|accessdate=2013-07-15}}</ref>，頒獎禮上她落實了她正於自己第三張專輯的初始階段，並為了[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]而逗留在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]時曾為新專輯進行一些會議，儘管她在此之前否認那些報導<ref name="newalbumconfirmation">{{Cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1538764/adele-talks-new-music-in-los-angeles |title=Adele Talks New Music in Los Angeles |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-10-19 |accessdate=2013-10-22 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012073623/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1538764/adele-talks-new-music-in-los-angeles |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/adele/68983|title=Adele says she'll record a new album when she 'has something to sing about'|publisher=[[新音乐快递|NME]]|accessdate=2014-01-18|date=2013-03-02|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060100/http://www.nme.com/news/adele/68983|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她還表示自己將很大機會與Paul Epworth再度合作<ref name="newalbumconfirmation"/>。根據報導，跟她合作製作新專輯的包括{{Link-en|湯姆·赫爾|Kid Harpoon}}、{{Link-en|詹姆斯·福特 (音樂家)|James Ford (musician)|詹姆斯·福特}}、{{Link-en|威廉·奧比|William Orbit}}、[[瑞安·特德|瑞安·特德]]和{{Link-en|黛安·華倫|Diane Warren}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/adele/69617|title=Adele back in the studio recording the follow-up to '21'?|publisher=NME|accessdate=2013-10-06|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061924/http://www.nme.com/news/adele/69617|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.co.uk/celebs/entertainment/ryan-tedder-adele-new-album|title=Adele is working on a new album and she’s sounding "even better than before"|publisher=Cosmopolitan UK|accessdate=2013-10-06|archive-date=2013-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007123239/http://www.cosmopolitan.co.uk/celebs/entertainment/ryan-tedder-adele-new-album|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.m-magazine.co.uk/carousel/interview-william-orbit/|title=Interview: William Orbit|publisher=m-magazine|accessdate=2013-11-28|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010322/http://www.m-magazine.co.uk/carousel/interview-william-orbit/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/21-things-to-get-excited-about-in-2014-2738/|title=21 things to get excited about in 2014|publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|last=Myers|first=Justin|date=2014-01-18|accessdate=2014-01-18|archive-date=2014-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121060701/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/21-things-to-get-excited-about-in-2014-2738/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而愛黛兒的發言人落實專輯將預計於2014年發行<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/salesmoss/status/419123927827230720|title=2014 going to be a good year for UK Music, Sande, ED Sheeran, Adele and Paolo Nutini are releasing ths year|last=Moss|first=Paul|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|accessdate=2014-01-26|archive-date=2014-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114084108/https://twitter.com/salesmoss/status/419123927827230720|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月24日的[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]，她獲得「最佳原創歌曲獎」並於頒獎禮上演唱<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-21570148 |title=Adele Skyfall wins best song Oscar |date=2013-02-25 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2013-02-25 |archive-date=2013-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225115203/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-21570148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年9月，[[維茲·卡利法|維茲·卡利法]]落實愛黛兒跟他合作製作他的第五張專輯《Blacc Hollywood》，雖然合作還有待清晰<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/125497/Wiz-Khalifa-Records-Adele-Collaboration-For-New-Album-Blacc-Hollywood |title=Wiz Khalifa Records Adele Collaboration For New Album 'Blacc Hollywood' |publisher=Entertainmentwise |date=2013-09-04 |accessdate=2013-10-22}}</ref>。2013年12月的《[[第56屆葛萊美獎|第56屆葛萊美獎]]》，愛黛兒獲得她的第13個[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]提名，包括「{{Link-en|葛萊美獎最佳創作影視媒體歌曲|Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media|最佳創作影視媒體歌曲}}」。

2014年1月26日，愛黛兒憑歌曲《Skyfall》於[[第56屆葛萊美獎|第56屆葛萊美獎]]上奪得「最佳創作影視媒體歌曲」獎項<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.grammy.com/nominees?genre=All |title=Annual GRAMMY Awards Nominees". |date=2013-12-06 |publisher=Grammy. |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208195133/http://www.grammy.com/Nominees?genre=All |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年5月的生日前夕，愛黛兒在她的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帳戶中發布一個隱晦的訊息，促使媒體對她下一張專輯的討論，該段訊息是：「25再見……下半年再見」，這個訊息由一些網站（例如[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]和[[首都電臺_(電臺網)|首都電臺]]）解讀，認為她的下一張專輯將會在2014年稍後的時間發布，專輯將定名為《[[25_(愛黛兒專輯)|25]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2620534/Adele-drops-biggest-hint-release-album-imminently.html |title=Bye bye 25... see you later in the year!': Adele drops biggest hint yet she is to release a third album imminently after cryptic tweet |date=2013-12-06 |publisher=Grammy. |accessdate=2013-12-06 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184349/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2620534/Adele-drops-biggest-hint-release-album-imminently.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/new-album-25-on-twitter |title=Eek! Adele’s New Album Is Complete And Set For A Surprise Release Like Beyonce’s! |publisher=Grammy. |date=2014-05-05 |accessdate=2014-05-05 |archive-date=2014-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505181801/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/adele/news/new-album-25-on-twitter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並預計於2015年11月20日發行<ref name="USiTunes">{{Cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/25/id1051394208|title=iTunes - Music - 25 by Adele|publisher=iTunes Store (US). Apple Inc.|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024063144/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/25/id1051394208|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，她獲[[世界音樂獎|世界音樂獎]]共9項的提名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://awardsandwinners.com/nominations/world-music-awards |title=World Music Awards Nominations 2014 |date=2014-06-07 |publisher=[[世界音樂獎|世界音樂獎]] |accessdate=2014-05-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812143729/http://awardsandwinners.com/nominations/world-music-awards/ |archivedate=2014-08-12 }}</ref>。

[[File:Adele_Live_2016_tour.jpeg|thumb]]表演，2016年3月]]
2015年10月23日，新專輯《[[25_(阿黛尔专辑)|25]]》的首支單曲《Hello》發行。11月，《25》正式推出，單單在美國首周銷量也突破338萬張，連同英國賣出的80萬張以及世界各地，首周全球總銷量合共超過400萬張。《25》遠超了[[宇多田光|宇多田光]]於2001年憑專輯《Distance》創下的史上最高首周全球總銷量紀錄。

2016年2月，確認第二支單曲為《When We Were Young》，2月24日在[[2016年全英音樂獎|2016年全英音樂獎]]中獲得「最佳英國女歌手」、「最佳英國專輯」《25》、「最佳英國單曲」《Hello》、「全球成就獎」4項大獎，成為當天的最大贏家，並在壓軸演唱歌曲《When We Were Young》。2016年5月22日，在[[美國|美國]][[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]舉行的2016[[告示牌音樂獎|告示牌音樂獎]]，愛黛兒榮獲「年度最佳藝人」、「最佳女歌手」、「最佳告示牌200大專輯榜歌手」、「最佳告示牌200大專輯」《25》、「最佳暢銷單曲」《Hello》5項大獎，愛黛兒因為進行世界巡迴演唱會緣故，所以未親臨領獎，但當天典禮中首映《Send My Love (To Your New Lover)》的MV，做為第三支單曲。

愛黛兒在2017年2月12日[[第59屆葛萊美獎|第59屆葛萊美獎]]典禮上，她五項提名再度橫掃囊括五獎，分別為「年度製作」/《Hello》、「年度專輯」/《25》、「年度歌曲」/《Hello》、「最佳流行歌手」/《Hello》與「最佳流行演唱專輯」/《25》，愛黛兒成為[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]有史以來首位二度完封，把所有入圍作品一次獲獎抱回的歌手。

2017年2月22日在[[全英音樂獎|2017年全英音樂獎]]中，愛黛兒再度蟬聯奪下「全球成就獎」。

=== 2018年至今：《30》 ===
2018年，消息指阿黛尔正创作个人第四张录音室专辑《[[30_(阿黛尔专辑)|30]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/everything-we-know-so-far-about-adeles-new-album-2343733 |title=Everything we know so far about Adele's new album |website=[[新音乐快递|NME]] |first=Ella |last=Braidwood |date=2018-06-25 |access-date=2018-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130161017/https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/everything-we-know-so-far-about-adeles-new-album-2343733 |archive-date=2018-11-30 |url-status=live }}</ref>。2019年5月5日31岁生日当天，阿黛尔在个人Instagram帐号发布多张黑白自拍照庆祝生日，回归上一年的工作。贴文结尾指出，《30》会是刁难大家的[[鼓打贝斯|鼓打贝斯]]专辑，让媒体猜测这是在暗示新专辑将要到来<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/adele-new-album-30-birthday-divorce-simon-konecki-a8901466.html|title=Adele teases her next album 30|date=2019-05-06|website=The Independent|access-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605205857/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/adele-new-album-30-birthday-divorce-simon-konecki-a8901466.html|archive-date=2019-06-05|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/30-will-be-a-drum-n-bass-record-to-spite-you-adele-teases-new-album-in-birthday-message-2484641|title="'30' will be a drum 'n' bass record to spite you" – Adele teases new album in birthday message|first=Damian|last=Jones|date=2019-05-06|website=NME|access-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506131321/https://www.nme.com/news/music/30-will-be-a-drum-n-bass-record-to-spite-you-adele-teases-new-album-in-birthday-message-2484641|archive-date=2019-05-06|url-status=live}}</ref>。2020年2月15日，阿黛尔在好友婚礼上宣布第四张专辑将于9月份面世<ref>{{cite news |title=Adele confirms new album set for release in September |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-confirms-new-album-set-for-release-in-september-2610085 |access-date=2020-02-17 |work=NME |archive-date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216221040/https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-confirms-new-album-set-for-release-in-september-2610085 |url-status=live }}</ref>，但后来确认专辑的制作与发行受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响延期<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/1165687/adele-s-new-album-won-t-be-released-anytime-soon-because-corona-ain-t-over|title=Adele's New Album Won't Be Released Anytime Soon Because ''Corona Ain't Over''|website=E! News|first=Pamela|last=Avila|date=2020-06-28|access-date=2020-06-29|archive-date=2020-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628224855/https://www.eonline.com/news/1165687/adele-s-new-album-won-t-be-released-anytime-soon-because-corona-ain-t-over|url-status=live}}</ref>。2020年10月24日，暌违电视荧幕四年的阿黛尔亮相《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》，与当晚的音乐表演嘉宾{{tsl|en|H.E.R.|H.E.R.}}共同出场<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-10-25|title=Adele sings and jokes about weight loss as she hosts Saturday Night Live|language=en-GB|publisher=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54680101|access-date=2020-10-25|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015223644/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54680101}}</ref>。

2021年10月1日，全球各大城市的地标及建筑出现数字“30”的投影及广告牌，不禁使人猜测阿黛尔在背后安排，认为《30》就是新专辑的名称<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/30-billboards-adele-1235641/|title=Do These Mysterious '30' Billboards Mean Adele Is Back?|first1=Jon|last1=Blistein|date=2021-10-01|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211007212606/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/30-billboards-adele-1235641/}}</ref>。不久后，阿黛尔的官方网站及社交媒体帐号发布和投影及广告牌设计相同的内容，暗示新专辑名字就是《30》<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rhyljournal.co.uk/news/national/uk-today/19624311.adele-teases-new-album-subtle-social-media-change/|title=Adele hints at new album after six years with subtle social media change|website=Rhyl Journal|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011005130/https://www.rhyljournal.co.uk/news/national/uk-today/19624311.adele-teases-new-album-subtle-social-media-change/}}</ref>，随后得到确认<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/adele-new-album-30-release-date-tracklist|title=Adele Says Many Songs On '30' Were Written For Her Son|first=Bria|last=McNeal|website=Nylon|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008030541/https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/adele-new-album-30-release-date-tracklist}}</ref>。2021年10月5日，阿黛尔宣布新单曲《[[寬容待我|寬容待我]]》，也是專輯裡首波主打歌曲，将于10月15日发布<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Skinner|first=Tom|date=2021-10-05|title=Adele announces comeback single 'Easy On Me', out next week|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-easy-on-me-single-teaser-listen-3062995|magazine=NME|access-date=2021-10-05|archive-date=2021-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011005128/https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-easy-on-me-single-teaser-listen-3062995}}</ref>。该曲获得如潮好评，发行当天打破Spotify和Amazon Music唱片播放量单日榜<ref>{{Cite magazine|title=Adele's 'Easy On Me' Dethrones BTS for Most-Streamed Song on Spotify in a Single Day|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9646113/adele-easy-on-me-most-streamed-song-spotify-record/|access-date=2021-10-16|magazine=Billboard|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105050311/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9646113/adele-easy-on-me-most-streamed-song-spotify-record/}}</ref>，同时空降英国单曲排行榜首位，是阿黛尔第三首英国冠军单曲，也是其个人2017年1月以来销量最高的歌曲<ref>{{cite news |title=Adele makes record-breaking Number 1 debut with Easy On Me |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adeles-easy-on-me-makes-record-breaking-number-1-debut-on-the-official-singles-chart__34286/ |access-date=2021-10-25 |agency=Official Charts Company |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104002450/https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adeles-easy-on-me-makes-record-breaking-number-1-debut-on-the-official-singles-chart__34286/ }}</ref>。歌曲还空降美国公告牌百强单曲榜冠军，是阿黛尔在美国的第五首冠军单曲<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9650488/hot-100-dated-10-30-top-10-story/|title=Adele's 'Easy on Me' Blasts to No. 1 on Billboard Hot 100|magazine=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2021-10-25|access-date=2021-10-26|archive-date=2021-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026094820/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9650488/hot-100-dated-10-30-top-10-story/}}</ref>。新专辑由[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]负责全球发行，而不是像以往那样由[[XL唱片|XL唱片]]和{{tsl|en|Beggars Group|乞丐集团}}负责海外发行，哥伦比亚负责北美发行<ref>{{Cite web|last=Paine|first=Andre|date=2021-10-13|title=Adele says Hello to Columbia Records UK, 30 album confirmed for November 19|url=https://www.musicweek.com/labels/read/adele-says-hello-to-columbia-records-uk-30-album-confirmed-for-november-19/084337|website=Music Week|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211013145548/https://www.musicweek.com/labels/read/adele-says-hello-to-columbia-records-uk-30-album-confirmed-for-november-19/084337}}</ref>。2021年11月19日，阿黛尔發布專輯第二波主打歌曲《[[我的天|我的天]]》，並於2022年1月13日推出該曲Music Video。

2022年2月8日在[[2022年全英音樂獎|2022年全英音樂獎]]中獲得「年度專輯」《30》、「年度歌手」、「年度單曲」《Easy On Me》等3項大獎，成為當天的最大贏家。

== 藝術性 ==
=== 聲線與音樂 ===
愛黛兒的音色被歸類為[[女低音|女低音]]。起初，評論人建議愛黛兒的聲線較她的曲詞創作更應成熟和更耐人尋味，這種多愁善感她也認同<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.westword.com/2009-01-22/music/despite-four-grammy-nominations-adele-is-figuring-out-how-to-be-herself/|title=Despite four Grammy nominations, Adele is figuring out how to be herself Westworld 21 January 2009|accessdate=2013-08-13|archive-date=2009-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122204728/http://www.westword.com/2009-01-22/music/despite-four-grammy-nominations-adele-is-figuring-out-how-to-be-herself/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她說：「我從聽[[艾拉·費茲潔拉|艾拉·費茲潔拉]]的歌來教導自己怎樣的唱歌技巧和音調，聽[[伊特·珍|伊特·珍]]的激情和{{Link-en|蘿貝塔·弗萊克|Roberta Flack}}的控制<ref>[http://myplay.com/artists/adele/bio "Adele Bio"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013224009/http://www.myplay.com/artists/adele/bio |date=2014-10-13 }}. Myplay direct. Sony Music Entertainment Inc. Retrieved 16 December 2012</ref>。」

愛黛兒的首張專輯《[[19_(專輯)|19]]》是以靈魂曲風貫穿，歌詞的字裡行間流露出感情破裂後的心碎與內心痛苦<ref name="BlogCriticsInterview">{{Cite web |url=http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/07/16/084115.php |title=Interview: Adele—Singer and Songwriter—Blogcritics Music |publisher=Blogcritics.org |accessdate=2011-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20090404132447/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/07/16/084115.php |archivedate=2009-04-04 }}</ref>，她成功同時躋身成為英國的靈魂女歌手之一，她們被形容為在美國音樂的《[[英國入侵|英國入侵]]》<ref name=collis/>。英國媒體逐漸封她作「新的[[艾美·懷恩豪斯|艾美·懷恩豪斯]]」<ref name=nicole/>，這然而她指懶得跟其他靈魂女歌手比較，說：「我們是一個性別，而不是一個類型<ref name="BlogCriticsInterview"/><ref name=MELISSARUGGIER/><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/dec/11/popandrock | title=Adele Guardian Interview | work=The Guardian | location=London | first=Hannah | last=Pool | date=2008-12-11 | accessdate=2010-04-23 | archive-date=2009-11-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091115163408/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/dec/11/popandrock | dead-url=no }}</ref>。」2009年初，聽眾與評論人開始形容愛黛兒與一般的靈魂歌手不同，她是獨一無二的，《全音樂》寫道，「愛黛兒比起任何人實在太神奇了<ref name=AmyWho/>，充滿魔力，無與倫比 」。

在發行首張專輯《19》後，[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]和[[碧昂絲·諾利斯|碧昂絲]]是在歌手中一致讚賞她的音樂的人<ref name="BlogCriticsInterview"/>，碧昂絲引述受到愛黛兒在她推出四張專輯《[[第4击|第4击]]》
是其中一位影響頗有的人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nme.com/news/beyonce/57054 |title=Beyonce inspired by Adele and Florence And The Machine on new album '4' |work=NME |location=UK |date=2011-06-03 |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-date=2011-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607034730/http://www.nme.com/news/beyonce/57054 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 [[瑪丹娜|瑪丹娜]]表示希望跟愛黛兒合作，說：「我覺得她是很出色的，我喜歡她<ref>{{Cite web |author=J J Anisiobi |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2131732/Madonna-I-love-work-Adele.html |title=Madonna: 'I would love to work with Adele' | Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2012-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620154348/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2131732/Madonna-I-love-work-Adele.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 」。

[[席琳·迪翁|席琳·迪翁]]於凱撒宮鬥獸場的表演中唱出《Rolling in the Deep》，之後告訴群眾，「我很喜歡愛黛兒，她真的很令人驚歎<ref>{{Cite news|first=David|last=Greenwald|title=Celine Dion Covers Adele at Vegas Show|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483346/celine-dion-covers-adele-at-vegas-show-listen|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=12 June|accessdate=2012-06-14|archive-date=2013-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130320103333/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/483346/celine-dion-covers-adele-at-vegas-show-listen|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。{{Link-en|扼殺者樂隊|The Stranglers}}的{{Link-en|讓-雅克·布魯內|Jean-Jacques Burnel}}稱自己也是一名樂迷，說：「她把我的目光集中在她身上……當然她是巨大的和她通常會把我關掉，因為她的歌太商業化了，但我真的深受感動<ref name="mojo_str">{{Cite web| author = Lindsay, Matthew| date = | url = http://www.mojo4music.com/blog/2012/02/stranglers_we_got_corrupted.html| title = We Got Corrupted| publisher = Mojo| accessdate = 2011-06-01| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130119042039/http://www.mojo4music.com/blog/2012/02/stranglers_we_got_corrupted.html| archivedate = 2013-01-19}}</ref>。」[[噴火戰機樂隊|噴火戰機樂隊]]的[[戴夫·格羅爾|戴夫·格羅爾]]和[[涅槃樂隊|涅槃樂隊]]在接受訪問時重複地讚賞愛黛兒<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|title=Foo Fighters' Dave Grohl: 'I'm glad we're competing with Adele at Grammys'|url=http://www.nme.com/news/foo-fighters/61920|publisher=[[新音乐快递|NME]]|date=2012-02-08|accessdate=2013-08-13|archive-date=2013-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923032723/http://www.nme.com/news/foo-fighters/61920|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Halperin|first=Shirley|title=Grammys 2012: Dave Grohl and Butch Vig Reflect on Nirvana, Adele and the State of the Music Business (Q&A)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dave-grohl-butch-vig-grammy-adele-nirvana-289304|publisher=Hollywood Reporter.|date=2012-02-10|accessdate=2013-08-13|archive-date=2013-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007235311/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dave-grohl-butch-vig-grammy-adele-nirvana-289304|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而戴夫·格羅爾認為《[[21_(專輯)|21]]》「具有空前的影響力，是一張難得的好專輯。它是那麼的真實，富有才華。它值得擁有一切它得到的讚美。這是一張偉大的專輯」。[[槍砲玫瑰|槍砲玫瑰]]的前結他手[[史萊許|史萊許]]指出：「她是非常好的，她是這個行業的鼓勵，她不造作的寫自己的歌，並設法出售以往的歌曲，這使她成為年輕藝人的一個好榜樣。<ref>[http://www.nme.com/news/slash/66405 Slash: 'Adele is a shot in the arm for music] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nme.com/news/slash/66405 |date=20121103045315 }}. NME. Retrieved 1 October 2012</ref>」

=== 影響 ===
愛黛兒最早受到英國騷靈歌手{{Link-en|露易絲·賈布里爾|Gabrielle (singer)}}的影響，當時5歲的愛黛兒一直很敬佩她，甚至在學校的才藝表演中戴上眼罩演出<ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=AQFtYLCVk0UC&pg=PT12&lpg=PT12&dq=adele+gabrielle+eye+patch&source=bl&ots=FsBP4ldXje&sig=xzuwN-3pqWjun1wD0RJ2TzOp9NM&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NUftUcXpOaHE0QW-joGIDg&ved=0CE0Q6AEwBA Adele: The Biography - Chas NewkeyBurden - Google Books] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=AQFtYLCVk0UC&pg=PT12&lpg=PT12&dq=adele+gabrielle+eye+patch&source=bl&ots=FsBP4ldXje&sig=xzuwN-3pqWjun1wD0RJ2TzOp9NM&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NUftUcXpOaHE0QW-joGIDg&ved=0CE0Q6AEwBA |date=20131001123353 }}. Books.google.co.uk (2011-10-27). Retrieved on 2013-07-24.</ref>。她指自己的音樂最大受到伊特·珍和碧昂絲的影響<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bluesandsoul.com/feature/302/the_futures_looking_rosie_for_adele/ |title=ADELE: Up close and personal |publisher=Bluesandsoul.com |date= |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2011-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708074331/http://www.bluesandsoul.com/feature/302/the_futures_looking_rosie_for_adele/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/497723/adele-talks-next-single-beyonce-collaboration-hopes |title=Adele Talks Next Single, Beyonce Collaboration Hopes |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-11-09 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2013-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527135753/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/497723/adele-talks-next-single-beyonce-collaboration-hopes |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她還表示她是聽[[辣妹合唱團|辣妹合唱團]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/video/hot-100-adele-on-the-spice-girls-471108 |title=Hot 100: Adele on the Spice Girls |publisher=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2013-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529144915/http://www.billboard.com/video/hot-100-adele-on-the-spice-girls-471108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[治療樂隊|治療樂隊]]及[[達斯蒂·斯普林菲爾德|達斯蒂·斯普林菲爾德]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nyunews.com/2013/03/14/adele/ |title=The Highlighter presents – Musical Influences: Adele |publisher=Nyunews.com |date=2013-03-14 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2013-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130903105023/http://nyunews.com/2013/03/14/adele/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和其他人的歌長大，她還稱跟她最親近的媽媽，向她透露了喜歡[[劳琳·希尔|劳琳·希尔]]、[[瑪麗·布萊姬|瑪麗·布萊姬]]和[[艾莉西亞·凱斯|艾莉西亞·凱斯]]，她們都讓愛黛兒得到啟發<ref>{{Cite web |author=By Toure |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-opens-up-about-her-inspirations-looks-and-stage-fright-20120210 |title=Adele Opens Up About Her Inspirations, Looks and Stage Fright: Pop's biggest voice of 2011 runs on cigarettes, red wine and high-octane heartbreak | Music News |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=2011-04-28 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2013-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727071315/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-opens-up-about-her-inspirations-looks-and-stage-fright-20120210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

愛黛兒說[[粉红佳人|粉红佳人]]是對她的音樂有最大影響的人，她在倫敦[[O2布里克斯頓學院|O2布里克斯頓學院]]看粉红佳人表演時是她生活中其中一個最決定的時間，說「那就是《Missundaztood》，那時我是13或14歲。我從來未聽過，在一間房中，有人在現場這樣的唱...我記得那種感覺就像是在個風洞一樣，她的聲音就像擊倒我似的，實在令人難以置信。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spinner.com/2010/12/23/adele-defining-moments/ |title=Adele – Defining Moments |publisher=Spinner |date=2010-12-23 |accessdate=2012-04-04 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130104194523/http://www.spinner.com/2010/12/23/adele-defining-moments/ |archivedate=2013-01-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=Name (Visible) |url=http://socialitelife.com/adele-says-hearing-pink-sing-changed-her-life-12-2010 |title=Adele Says Hearing Pink Sing Changed Her Life |publisher=Socialite Life |date=2010-12-23 |accessdate=2012-04-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325203234/http://socialitelife.com/adele-says-hearing-pink-sing-changed-her-life-12-2010 |archivedate=2012-03-25 }}</ref> 」

